Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:48.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hey, let's just swim with our clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hop{\fncinnamon cake}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}A spiral of sensational temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:56.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Those beats that sting me are strange
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}They burn out and disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I'm fine with those crazy days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Dress up
