Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What's that dance called{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Don't go, it lingers on  in my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Melody is
