Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.32,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.99,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{\an8}So tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:46.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I really keep these?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's probably a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.76,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mukae!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.24,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.16,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.39,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.28,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.88,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Morning, Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:04.77,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:07.04,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.27,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not gonna get my hopes up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.06,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've already been rejected once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.70,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Can I get the usual, Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.91,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.89,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.45,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're looking beautiful as always, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.76,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.21,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.05,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.88,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're in shock over the news that Yurika eloped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.43,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's all over the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,D-Did you tell him about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.08,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, Kawabuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:47.89,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Yep, I told him this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.81,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I don't think he's in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect to hear anything like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.07,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.44,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,Ah, that's the piece that won the Governor's Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.70,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,We'd better take it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.30,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,You take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:26.24,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,The school doesn't want to display a painting done by someone involved in a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.13,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,We were told to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And what's going to happen to it after you take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.69,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.36,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This painting is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.54,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,What's she to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.24,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,Had eyes for her, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.68,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Let it go, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You can take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.55,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.78,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You don't care about it at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.01,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.10,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Your stupidity must be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:16.89,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Seriously, how stupid are you gonna be for somebody else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.69,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.71,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What about her painting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.13,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, I already said goodbye to it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.32,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.31,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:40.06,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did a certain someone give you a gift recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Like something that was knitted maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.54,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:49.85,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(150,350)}I knitted Sentaro a sweater and used the leftover yarn to make your mittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}So cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.90,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Look! It's called Lily-yarn or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.18,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I got it from Sachiko yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Nope. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:06.11,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But what am I supposed to do with a string?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:07.33,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:13.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:16.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.08,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.33,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait up, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.38,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:34.92,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,U-Um, these are really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ow! Dammit! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.03,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Nope, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.87,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we'll be changing classes again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.37,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess third-years are split up by their grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.50,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so you probably won't be in the same class as Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.89,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Goin' for college entrance exams, right Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.33,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I intend to go to college, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:13.03,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about becoming an elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.67,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,So you're gonna be a teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.31,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:21.73,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Long time ago, you said you wanted to have a bakery or a cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.55,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.31,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.30,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Come on, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You were a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.60,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,So you wanted a shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.49,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.04,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, where do you want to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.16,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,As for me, never mind about college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.06,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I might not even make it to next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait, what did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.22,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, it all comes down to the next makeup exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Start with these basic problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll make you some flash cards in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.19,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm just not cut out for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if you fail this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.57,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll just quit school an' get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You must be jo—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.51,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,It ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.33,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I've thought about my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.59,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't afford to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.25,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.76,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you flunk this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:50.78,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.07,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait! You're right in the middle of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.20,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.53,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If you're going to rest, it'll have to wait 'til you're done with these problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.63,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't! My head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.47,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,B-Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:20.81,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You always look so happy when you're surrounded by children.{This could be taken the wrong way...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.77,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I bet you're going to have a big family of your own,{Well, he is Catholic...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,with lots of kids around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It'll be a warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.82,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Chi'ko wet herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yay, Chi'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.27,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,The bath's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.83,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,My mom will dry your pants, so relax for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is an unusual setup for a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:08:59.22,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.02,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're out of soap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.88,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Here... {reverse misunderstandings}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.74,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Isn't this Sen's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.75,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,We share a bath with Sentaro's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:33.63,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Y'know... I wish I had given the mittens to you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.24,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's almost spring, so you won't need to use them anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:47.65,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'd wear them all year 'round, since {\i1}you{\i0} knitted them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:49.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.15,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.65,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.15,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro lets out a yelp once in a while himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Say, Ritsu, why did you give me those mittens, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.30,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.92,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why me and not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.74,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.30,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If you've liked him all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:33.98,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.03,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,How about havin' dinner here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.82,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Your pants aren't dry yet anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.49,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.87,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait, your hair's soakin' wet! You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:46.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.29,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.30,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't mean to say that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.35,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I couldn't get it out of my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:13.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}She probably still has feelings for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.87,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sen, how did the makeup exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, you passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:30.75,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.44,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.09,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.00,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I gotta thank 'im proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.82,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen Richie-rich much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.44,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,He passed out in class with a fever the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.05,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so he's restin' up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.56,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.58,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Nope, Ritsuko didn't say a thing.{God I love his voice}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.21,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,"Someday My Prince Will Come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.12,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.55,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko. Wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Huge, ain't it? That's Richie's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.65,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Thank Richie for me, for helpin' me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.55,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.39,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:39.98,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.99,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:49.43,Default,Aunt,0,0,0,,Kaoru, one of your classmates has come to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.37,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.79,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, is your fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.59,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry to make you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.07,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I see. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.52,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.97,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Eat them if you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.48,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you go out of the way to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.36,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I didn't buy these. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.00,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.01,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He came here with you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I saw you two from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.77,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He should've come in with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.50,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Never mind. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.06,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.27,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You two have been together since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.51,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,There's no way I could be a match for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:57.52,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Unlike me, he's strong and built...{He's ripped...I'm not...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.52,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And he's so handsome, he even takes my breath away once in a while...{Gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:05.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're better off with him, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:06.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:14.11,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I know what you're saying, so please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.50,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:28.27,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, don't you like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.51,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Or is it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:34.09,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,that you just don't have any confidence, so you're trying to keep your distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:39.77,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, you told me to have confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:44.27,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Those words have saved me a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:48.67,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But if it looks like you don't have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.15,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I have a feeling I'll lose mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.29,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:06.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,350)}What I've wished for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.20,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,Oh, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.18,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.51,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! I bet something happened between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.69,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.20,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll go over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.84,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let me tell you how I feel about you once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.85,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you, Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.12,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you! {\alpha&HFF&}I love you! I love you! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.69,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\an8}K-Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:00.92,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you! {\alpha&HFF&}I love you! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.95,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you! I love you! {\alpha&HFF&}I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.35,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you! I love you! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\an8}P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.19,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your family can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:17.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not muscular and maybe I'm not as manly as I could be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:22.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but when it comes to my feelings for you, I'm second to none!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:29.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I might get you sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.08,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.01,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:42.10,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Hey! You're burning up! And you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.94,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.28,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was really something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.02,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru! Anyone, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.33,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's summer already and I haven't made any more progress with Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though I was so bold when I had a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me when I'm not sick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.84,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I want to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.18,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Touch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How long have you been in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:13.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.53,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.56,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.80,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.93,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.8\fs30\fnAver\b1\c&H000001&\org(1145,207)\pos(1125,208)\frx20\fry6\frz330.5}East High
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.93,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fscx90\fs30\fnAver\b1\c&H000001&\frz324.3\frx4\fry346\pos(834,578)}Newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.93,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,"The Olympus Has Thrown Down the Gauntlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:28.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,"The Olympus is going to win at this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:32.03,Default,Kaoru to Seiji,0,0,0,,It seems there are still some old-fashioned jazz musicians around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.59,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,but this is the era of rock 'n' roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,They were handing this out all over the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.53,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.65,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't take this sitting down, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.58,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You two are gonna perform in the festival, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:46.74,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.09,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:56.04,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,We start with "Moanin'" to fire up the people who saw us last year
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.84,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,an' fake 'em out thinking we're gonna do the same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.14,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But then we move into some other songs that we want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I was thinkin' the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.35,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right, let's choose our next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.91,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Startin' today, we'd better practice every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:10.81,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:12.91,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.98,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.36,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.01,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.01,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Look, I got big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Dad says he's comin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This way, the whole family can live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.09,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.13,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.74,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I can't say that I'm actually scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.61,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,See, our Dad was working really far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.61,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,And he's coming home tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:02.53,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, I'm one of those that ain't got a place in his own home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.46,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.20,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.59,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, you're back late, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.10,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's Richie doin' here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.39,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Unlike with Kota and the other little ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.98,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,you remember how scary Dad was when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.92,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But don't worry, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:37.11,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ma told me that Dad worked really hard an' quit drinkin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.24,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. You got nothin' to worry about, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Now how about comin' inside an' we can get ready together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.79,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:55.50,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for lookin' after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:59.51,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're the one I'm worried about, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Dope! What're you lookin' so serious for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.81,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What?! I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.82,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie. Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.20,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.56,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:23.41,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:23.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you coming to practice tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:34.66,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. After all, playin' jazz with you is the most fun I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, what are you writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hmm... Nah, that's no good.
